      <br><strong><h3>BACKGROUND</h3></strong><br>
      <br>NYU uses tax free bond money to reimburse money spent on ongoing building maintenance and construction projects. <br><br> To avoid regulation violations, Treasury users currently work in a legacy system to manage bonds and generate reports and requests.<br><br>
