      <strong><h3>GOALS</h3></strong><br><br>
          1. To present complex data in a way that is (1) easy to understand and comprehend and (2) easier on the eyes so that users can focus on making decisions central to their workflow.<br><br>
          2. To minimize manual data entry for Treasury users.<br><br>
          3. To augment this solutions package with a front end design for an enhanced user experience.
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5ths">
    </div>
